WEBVTT

00:03.440 --> 00:06.680
We're called 
 the Midnight Society.

00:06.680 --> 00:09.800
[COYOTE HOWLING]

00:11.240 --> 00:15.360
Separately, we're very different. 
 We like different things,

00:15.360 --> 00:20.160
We go to different schools, 
 and we have different friends.

00:20.160 --> 00:23.160
But one thing draws us together--

00:23.160 --> 00:25.880
The dark.

00:25.880 --> 00:28.800
Each week, 
 we gather around this fire

00:28.800 --> 00:33.680
To share our fears 
 and our strange and scary tales.

00:33.680 --> 00:36.280
It's what got us together,

00:36.280 --> 00:39.840
and it's what keeps 
 bringing us back.

00:39.840 --> 00:42.920
This is a warning to all who join us--

00:42.920 --> 00:45.840
you're going to leave 
 the comfort of the light...

00:47.720 --> 00:51.760
And step into the world 
 of the supernatural.

00:55.880 --> 00:57.160
Watch your step.

00:57.160 --> 00:59.720
- Hey, watch it, man! 
 - I'm sorry.

00:59.720 --> 01:01.520
Frank Moore, 
 you're here to be considered

01:01.520 --> 01:03.280
as a new member of 
 the Midnight Society.

01:03.280 --> 01:04.560
Yeah, what's with the blindford?

01:04.560 --> 01:06.680
This meeting place is a secret.

01:06.680 --> 01:08.720
Yeah, and you're not in yet.

01:08.720 --> 01:11.920
- [FRANK] Swell. 
 - Who sponsors, Frank?

01:11.920 --> 01:13.840
I do. 
 He's a good guy.

01:13.840 --> 01:15.880
Yeah, but can he tell a good story?

01:15.880 --> 01:18.400
Who said that?

01:18.400 --> 01:20.280
To be a member, you have 
 to tell us a scary tale.

01:20.280 --> 01:23.400
Then we vote, and it has 
 to be unanimous or you're not in.

01:23.400 --> 01:25.960
- You ready? 
 - Yeah. I'm ready.

01:25.960 --> 01:29.400
- Are you guys ready? 
 - Ohh!  - Ohh!

01:29.400 --> 01:31.600
I'm scared now. Ooh!

01:37.080 --> 01:38.960
Yo, take this thing off.

01:38.960 --> 01:41.640
Sorry. 
 Not unless you get in.

01:41.640 --> 01:45.360
You're the sponsor, Dave. 
 You got to start it.

01:46.720 --> 01:49.440
Remember how to do it?

01:49.440 --> 01:52.480
[FRANK] 
 Just say the word.

01:52.480 --> 01:55.640
Anytime. 
 OK, let's do it.

01:55.640 --> 01:59.680
Submitted for the approval, 
 of the Midnight Society,

01:59.680 --> 02:01.840
I call this story...

